---
import IconInstagram from '~icons/mdi/instagram'
import IconGitHub from '~icons/mdi/github'
import IconEmail from '~icons/mdi/email'
import IconIUT from '~icons/local/iut'
import IconBiome from '~icons/local/biome'
import MdiCardsHeart from '~icons/mdi/cards-heart'
---
<footer class="bg-black text-white p-8 md:p-18 gap-12 md:gap-24 flex flex-col">
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 max-w-[500px] w-full">
      <h2 class="uppercase text-xl md:text-4xl font-600 tracking-widest">
        Nos réseaux
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base tracking-wider">
        Retrouvez nous sur ces diverses plateformes pour toujours être au courant des dernières nouveautés !
      </p>
  
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-4xl mt-6 text-white/60">
        <a
          href="https://instagram.com/oeil_limoges"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="hover:text-white"
          title="Instagram"
        >
          <IconInstagram class="hover:text-white transition-colors" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/OeilAssociationLimoges"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="hover:text-white"
          title="GitHub"
        >
          <IconGitHub class="hover:text-white transition-colors" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:asso.oeil@gmail.com"
          class="hover:text-white"
          title="E-Mail"
        >
          <IconEmail class="hover:text-white transition-colors" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 max-w-[500px] w-full">
      <h2 class="uppercase text-xl md:text-4xl font-600 tracking-widest">
        L'IUT
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base tracking-wider">
        À noter que ce site n'est pas affilié à l'IUT du Limousin.
      </p>
  
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-4xl mt-6 text-white/60">
        <a
          href="https://biome.unilim.fr"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="hover:text-white"
          title="Biome"
        >
          <IconBiome class="hover:text-white transition-colors" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.iut.unilim.fr"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="hover:text-white"
          title="IUT de Limoges"
        >
          <IconIUT class="hover:text-white transition-colors" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-white/60 mt-8 flex text-xs sm:text-base items-center gap-1 sm:gap-2 flex-wrap">
    Développé avec <MdiCardsHeart class="text-white" /> par <a class="text-white hover:text-white/80 hover:underline hover:underline-offset" href="https://github.com/Vexcited">Mikkel ALMONTE--RINGAUD</a> pour l'OEIL.
  </p>
</footer>